# iOS QuadController Programming Guidelines

- After you are finished making changes to the iOS project, please make sure to
  always try and build the project. You can do so using the following command:

- Run the following command and make sure it emits `"BUILD SUCCEEDED"`:

```
xcodebuild build \
  -project QuadController.xcodeproj \
  -scheme QuadController \
  -sdk iphonesimulator \
  -configuration Debug
```
